.TH XGAMEOFLIFE 6 "Jun 29, 2022"
.SH NAME
xgameoflife \- conway's game of life.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBxgameoflife\fP [ -hv ] [ -l FILE ]
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
show the help message and exit
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
display the program version
.TP
\fB\-l\fR, \fB\-\-load\fR
load saved board
.SH CONTROLS
.TP
\fBmiddle click\fR
move around
.TP
\fBleft click\fR
toggle hovered cell
.TP
\fBwheel up/down\fR
zoom in/out
.TP
\fBspace\fR
pause/resume
.TP
\fBn\fR
advance to next generation
.TP
\fBctrl + s\fR
save board
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
\fB0\fR
the program terminated successfully
.TP
\fB1\fR
an error occurred
